{"tid":1537114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"『行動』強制性罷鐵計劃開始啦","createTime":"2019-09-03T21:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T22:02:31.000Z","uid":152321,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7eb4173f1a0d6e6348e2a26d9bfc0ff18a71e68b","tid":1537114,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T21:22:09.000Z","msg":"呢個post主要目的係俾全城免車費，繼而減少黨鐵收入，懲罰黨鐵。<br />\n<br />\n我想講其實最有效嘅方法係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">爆閘機</span><br />\n<br />\n一： 快 10分鐘內可以做冧一個細站<br />\n二： 成本低 任何液體，甚至膨漲膠，鎚仔等<br />\n三： 對全港市民零影響 大家免交通費<br />\n四： 唔需要大量人手 10個到已經可以做冧一個細站<br />\n五： 零危險 無狗守就想捉都捉唔到<br />\n六： 參予率高 無閘想俾錢都唔得<br />\n七： 回復率高 一晚整返好？俾10分鐘我再爆過<br />\n八： 唔會失民意 For民意撚only<br />\n九： 配合好可以變相塞鐵 只爆細站閘 不爆大站閘試想一下 一個無跳過閘，一個普通市民 當要被逼唔嘟卡入閘 但係要嘟卡出閘個陣會有幾驚 係罪惡感嘅逼使之下 佢地就會去補飛(除非肯跳閘) <br />\n<br />\n壞處味諗到<br />\n<br />\n一個人補飛好小事 不值一提<br />\n但係當一千個人去補飛嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />molamola <br />\n如果你趕時間 前面又有幾百個人排隊 要點算好？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">跳閘囉</span><br />\n<br />\n我相信跳過閘嘅人都知跳閘 係會上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要好多時候得自己一個跳 <br />\n但係當十個人 一百個人 甚至一百萬人跳嘅時候 <br />\n交通費再不存在<br />\n<br />\n係全港戒嚴嘅情況下，手足們都好難發起啲大型，甚至中型行動。係呢個情況下，我地只能化整為零，由一團熊熊烈烈嘅自由之火，化為滿城火光，遍地開花，真真正正嘅星星之火，為未來嘅燎原之勢凖備。<br />\n<br />\n呢一個行動 我希望可以俾到大家一個想法 <br />\n雖然人多好辦事<br />\n但係人少都可以做到人多做唔到嘅嘢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聚為冰 散如水</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地話我地係曱甴？<br />\n好！我地就化為曱甴 我地要令你後悔稱我地為曱甴<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">恐龍絕種 曱甴不滅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人 加油</span></span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"745320364e95d46125ba8ec917dfb1195099da86","tid":1537114,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T21:22:28.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"e61c5820ff87ee4b17565546574f0b30c3a83f51","tid":1537114,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T21:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75729831a51796e9387d0bd78d62842482b29c4","tid":1537114,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T21:23:04.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"2afb3137fd13ed558cf56cddf8071389ac1e1585","tid":1537114,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T21:23:14.000Z","msg":"人呢"},{"pid":"2cfaa3b0a82dbfa9ce820e19cf94642af8c44be3","tid":1537114,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T21:24:00.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"59265c9c0c54257e9ae331bdf03177eb9c89be85","tid":1537114,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T21:24:24.000Z","msg":"唔係得我一個訓唔着呀"},{"pid":"4f453829cf162eee1a778abba2425604cfa33f05","tid":1537114,"uid":265949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T21:24:37.000Z","msg":"gogogo"},{"pid":"12b833c371c315868d13ede6e5c3535d9eae79e6","tid":1537114,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T21:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46288d2cc621a46b87a6005f5fb60e3216ba9e87","tid":1537114,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T21:25:03.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"2601d50f4db54f9fd58afe2fc74f80f24f601ca6","tid":1537114,"uid":137265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,